Title: QED x QCD Resummation and Shower/ME Matching for LHC Physics
Authors: B.F.L. Ward and S.A. Yost
Categories: hep-ph
Comments: 12 pages, LaTex with packages amsmath, amssymb
Report-no: BU-HEPP-07/02
Journal-ref: ActaPhys.Polon.B38:2395-2403,2007
\\
  We present the theory of QED x QCD resummation and its interplay with
shower/matrix element matching in precision LHC physics scenarios. We
illustrate the theory using single heavy gauge boson production at hadron
colliders.
